\c[27]A tentacle emerged from the shadows and
leapt at Rio with vigor, wrapping around her...!

\c[27]Taken by surprise, Rio was a bit startled...
but once she understood the situation, she didn't
resist and let the tentacle wrap around her
freely.

\c[27]\n<Rio>"Hmm... you're the first one to commemorate this
occasion, huh?"

\c[27]\n<Rio>"Mmm~... I've been caught...\i[93], so... what
will you do now? ...with me... my... thing..."

\c[27]The tentacle wrapped around her entire body,
almost completely restricting Rio's movements.

\c[27]However, Rio didn't panic at all; instead,
she looked at the tentacle wrapped around her with
eyes shining with anticipation...

\c[27]As if to meet Rio's expectations, a tentacle
shaped like a male genital appeared out of nowhere
and rubbed against Rio's face.

\c[27]Rio, not at all displeased, smiled as she
rubbed her cheek against the lewdly shaped
tentacle.

\c[27]\n<Rio>"Ah... ha... such an obvious shape...\i[93] It's a
simple type for a monster, but not bad at all...
hehe...\i[93]"

\c[27]The tentacle rubbing against her face pulsed
vigorously...! It grew harder and began to curve
upwards dramatically...!

\c[27]\n<Rio>"Haah... haah... ah... that's amazing...\i[93] I
can feel its excitement... coming
through...\i[93]"

\c[27]\n<Rio>"If something like that were to stir inside me...
both my front and back would be completely wrecked
together... haah... haah...\i[93]"

\c[27]Rio's breathing became more intense as she
whispered words mixed with desire in her
breaths...

\c[27]Just as Rio's inner expectations seemed to
reach their peak...

\c[27]The tentacle that had been rubbing against
Rio's cheek couldn't withstand the sensation of
her skin and ejaculated.

\c[27]A large amount of semen was released onto
Rio's face, leaving her momentarily stunned...

\c[27]But then she quickly sensed something and
her expression turned into one of understanding as
she smiled and extended her tongue to lick the
semen dripping down to her mouth.

\c[27]\n<Rio>"Mmm~... it's thinner than I thought...\i[93]
Well, it was a simple type after all, so this is
probably about right\i[93]"

\c[27]\n<Rio>"Ah~ what a pity you couldn't last until the
'end'... But I guess it's mutual..."

\c[27]\n<Rio>"Hehe, there's no shame in cumming from a face rub
like this, you know? There have been plenty before
you... both humans and monsters alike...\i[93]"

\c[27]As the tentacle twitched in the afterglow of
its climax, Rio calmly licked off the semen while
speaking as if talking to it.

\c[27]\n<Rio>"Well, it looks like there will be plenty of
opportunities for fun, so this is fine for now I
guess...\i[93]"

\c[27]It seemed that Rio had achieved some level
of satisfaction as she slowly began to untangle
herself from the loosened grip of the tentacle.

\c[27]Before the tentacle could move again, Rio
expertly made her escape.

\c[27]Taking some distance, Rio faced the tentacle
again, her expression already back to that of a
"demon exterminator."
